Chapter 5
Methodology
Data Cleaning
Missing value handling
Duplicate removal
Data normalization
Text Preprocessing
Lowercase conversion
Tokenization
Stop-word removal
Lemmatization
Feature Engineering

Two techniques were used.

Bag of Words

Converts text into word frequency vectors.

TF-IDF

Assigns importance weights to words based on frequency and rarity.

Similarity Measurement

Cosine Similarity calculates similarity between TF-IDF vectors.

Chapter 6
