Recommendation Statistics

Chapter 7
Recommendation Engine

Algorithm

User selects a book.
Combined text is created.
TF-IDF vectors are generated.
Cosine similarity matrix is computed.
Similar books are ranked.
Top-N recommendations are displayed.
Chapter 8
Results

The recommendation system successfully recommends books based on textual similarity.

Example

Input

